[/color][/i][/b]             [size=6]Elise is a Assassin based follower and she is standalone so you don't need anything other than the armor mod for Elise i will have a link for it down in the OPTIONAL list.

[b][i][color=#ead1dc][img]http://i.imgur.com/Vuutci4.png[/img]

[/color][/i][/b][size=6]To install the mod manually here are the steps to show you how to install it manually.

[/size][size=5]1. Locate your skyrim data folder normally it's here (C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\Skyrim\Data)
[/size]

[size=5]2.Put the files inside the rar to into the skyrim data folder.

3.Now you got the mod installed. Good job
